[{"Id": 1012136, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "Imam Reza (a) is reported as saying: If one observes fasting on the last 3 days of Sha’ban and attaches it to the obligatory fasting of Ramazan, Almighty Allah will decide him as having observed fasting for two consecutive months.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Imam Reza (a) ne farmaya, agar koi Shaban ke aakhri 3 dino mein roza rakkhe aur usey Mahe Ramazan ke waajib rozo’n se muttasil kare (mila) de, to Allah (swt) usey 2 mahine ke roze shumaar karega.", "UrduDescription": "امام علی رضا ؑسے منقول ہے : جو شخص شعبان کےآخری تین دن روزہ رکھ کر ماہِ رمضان کے روزوں سے متصل کردے تو حق تعالیٰ اس کے نامۂ اعمال میں دو مہینے متصل روزوں کا ثواب لکھے گا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012137, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 2, "EnglishDescription": "Abul-Salt al-Harawi has narrated that when he visited Imam Reza (a) on the last Friday of Sha’ban, the Imam said to him: the days of Sha’ban have almost passed. This is the last Friday. You should thus settle what you have missed in this month by working harder in the rest of it. You may supplicate God, implore for His forgiveness, recite the Holy Qur’an, and repent to Him from your sins so that you receive the month of Ramazan with pure sincerity to Him. You must fulfill all the trusts that you are liable to settle, do not bear malice against any of your brethren in-faith, you must give up any sin that you commit. Fear Almighty Allah and trust in Him in secret and openly, for ‘If anyone puts his trust in Allah, sufficient is (Allah) for him. For Allah will surely accomplish his purpose. Verily, for all things has Allah appointed a due proportion.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Abul-Salt al-Harawi se riwaayat hai keh jab woh Imam Reza (a) se mulaqaat ke liye Shaban ke aakhri Juma ko gaye, to Imam (a) ne unhe farmaya: Ziyadah-tar Shaban ke din guzar gaye. Yeh aakhri Juma hai. Tumhe chahiye keh tum se jo kuchh chhoot gaya hai usey bache huwe dino mein ziyadah koshish kar ke pura kare. Tum Allah se dua karo, Istghefaar karo, Tilaawate Qur’an karo, aur Allah (swt) se maafi talab karo ta-keh mahe Ramazan ko tum paak o paakeeza haalaat mein pa sako’n. Jo bhi maamle mein taqraar ho usko hal karo, koi bhi momin se takraar mat karo, jo gunah tum karte huwe aaye ho usey tark kar do. Allah (swt) se dara karo aur us par bharosa karo akele mein aur manzare aam mein, keh agar koi Allah (swt) par bharosa karega to Allah (swt) uske liye kaafi hai. Allah (swt) yaqeenan uski haajat ko pura karega, be-shak, har cheez ke liye Allah (swt) ne ek waqt ko moayyan kiya huwa hai.", "UrduDescription": "ابوصلت ہروی سے روایت ہے : میں شعبان کے آخری جمعہ کو امام علی رضا ؑ کی خدمت میں حاضر ہوا تو حضرتؑ نے مجھ سے فرمایا: اے ابوصلت! شعبان کا زیادہ حصہ گزرگیا ہے اور آج اس کاآخری جمعہ ہے۔لہٰذا اس کے گزشتہ دنوں میں تجھ سے جو کوتاہیاں ہوئی ہیں اس کے باقی آنے والے دنوں میں تجھے ان کی تلافی (بھرپائی) کرلینی چاہیےاور تمہیں وہ عمل اختیار کرنا چاہیےجو تمہارے لئے مفید ہو، تمہیں تلاوتِ قرآن اور بہت زیادہ دعا وا ستغفار کرنا چاہیے نیز خدا کی بارگاہ میں اپنے گناہوں پر توبہ کرو تا کہ جب ماہِ مبارک رمضان آئے تو اس وقت تک تم نے خود کو اپنے رب کے لئے خالص کرلیا ہو۔ اپنے ذمہ کسی کا کوئی حق نہ رہنے دو مگر یہ کہ اسے ادا کردو، اپنے دل میں کسی کے لئے بغض و کینہ نہ رکھو۔ اگر کوئی گناہ کرتے رہے ہو تو اسے ترک کردو، خدا سے ڈرو اور ظاہر و باطن میں اسی پر بھروسہ رکھو جوشخص خدا پر توکل اور بھروسہ رکھتا ہے تو خدا اس کے لئے کافی ہے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012138, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 3, "EnglishDescription": "In the rest days of Shaban, you may repeat the following zikr very much for Almighty Allah saves many people from Hellfire on account of the sanctity of this month…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Shaban ke baaqi dino mein, tumhe chahiye keh is zikr ko jitna ho sakey dauraaye, keh Allah (swt) is mahine ki barkat se kahi logo’n ko Jahannam ki aag se azaad karta hai…", "UrduDescription": "اس مہینے کے باقی دنوں میں زیادہ تر یہ دعا پڑھا کرو، کیوں کہ حق تعالیٰ اس مہینے میں احترامِ رمضان کی خاطر اپنے بہت زیادہ بندوں کوجہنم کی آگ سے آزاد فرماتا ہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012139, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah: If You have not forgiven us in the past days of Sha`ban, (please do) forgive us in the rest of it.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Agar Tu ne hamein Shaban ke guzishta dino mein gunaho’n ki maafi nahi di to abhi iske baaqi dino mein hamein bakhshish ataa kar de.", "Urdu": "اے معبود!اگر تو نے ہمیں شعبان کے گزشتہ دنوں میں گناہوں کی معافی نہیں دی تو بھی اس کے باقی دنوں میں ہمیں بخشش عطا کردے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA IN LAM TAKUN GHAFAR-TA LANAA FEE-MAA MANAA MIN SHA’BAANA FAGH-FIR LANAA FEE-MAA BAQEYA MINHO.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنْ لَمْ تَكُنْ غَفَرْتَ لَنَا فِيْمَا مَضٰى مِنْ شَعْبَانَ فَاغْفِرْ لَنَا فِيْمَا بَقِيَ مِنْهُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "Arabic